abstract: Notre Dame and NBC Sports reached a deal Thursday guaranteeing that the university’s home football games will remain on the network through the 2015 season.
snippet: Notre Dame and NBC Sports reached a deal Thursday guaranteeing that the university’s home football games will remain on the network through the 2015 season.
lead_paragraph: For the fourth time since they vowed to love and honor each other in 1990, Notre Dame and NBC Sports renewed their television vows on Thursday, guaranteeing that the university’s home football games will remain on the network through the 2015 season.
